<h1 id="conclusion">Conclusion</h1>
<p>So after using this client side rendering concepts and stacks for about a year, i found out that:</p>
<h3 id="best-use-cases-for-ssr-and-dssr">best use cases for SSR and DSSR</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Landing page or websites that doesnâ€™t require any data input and outputs</li>
  <li>Blogs and Forums</li>
  <li>Web Apps that requires good compatibility with SEO</li>
  <li>Load Time</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="best-use-cases-for-csr">best use cases for CSR</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Web Apps that doesnâ€™t care about SEO, good examples are web apps used on business end</li>
  <li>Load Time (Client will have bad experience if slow internet connection is involved)</li>
  <li>No full page reload, as the only thing that needs to load is the APIâ€™s data</li>
</ul>

